list.abstract: 《Mean》是一首由Taylor Swift（泰勒·斯威夫特）作词、作曲并演唱的一首英语流行歌曲，2010年10月25日发行，收录在专辑《Speak Now》中。 《Mean》囊括歌词的抒情细节和深厚的乡村音乐声音，并得到了正面的评价。这首歌也在澳大利亚音乐榜单上得到第45号的名次。泰勒凭借此曲第一次在乡村音乐协会奖以及2011年4月3日的第46届奥斯卡大奖上演出。在第54届格莱美奖颁奖典礼上，歌曲赢得了最佳乡村歌曲和最佳乡村独唱两项大奖。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. What I mean is, okay. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，我的意思是，我同意，是的。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, millions of people are gonna buy this machine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的意思是说，上百万的人正在等着买我们的机器

yingyinNormal.en: No, I didn't mean that I got against you. No, of course I do mean that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的意思是我没有不喜欢你，实际上我就是那个意思。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, synchronized swimming. I mean, the balance beam. Help me. Football. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是说，水上芭蕾（还是女子运动项目）我的意思是，平衡木（仍旧是女子运动项目）帮帮忙.橄榄球! 谢了。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you making an offer? I mean, no, l would not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是在出价吗? 不，我的意思是，当然不卖。

yingyinNormal.en: No, Mike. No, no, you wanna pick me. I mean.. Watch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不, 迈克, 不。选我!我的意思是, 瞧!

yingyinNormal.en: I mean there's gonna be times where your eyes are uneven.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意思是有时候你的眼部皮肤不均匀。

yingyinNormal.en: How do you know that? Why does Elrond mean secret meeting?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么知道的？为什么爱隆的意思是秘密会议？

yingyinNormal.en: Does that mean money? It might. Well, I'll get right on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 意思是有钱赚吗？有可能。好，我马上办。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, what do you mean? It means they're blaming the victim.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么意思？意思是他们把责任推卸到受害人身上。

yingyinNormal.en: You mean, like a party? Yeah, right. A party. What do you say?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的意思是？是派对吧？是的,很对，是派对，你怎么说？

yingyinNormal.en: So it's like the long haul? What do you mean the "Long haul"? I mean the long haul that you're gonna stay in this band for a long time. On tour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以这就像持久战？你说“持久战”什么意思？我说持久战的意思是你得待在这个乐队里一直巡回演出。就像一场持久战。

yingyinNormal.en: What does that mean? It means Lady Mary knows what she's about.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么意思？意思是，玛丽小姐知道自己的心意。

yingyinNormal.en: You mean you only see me as a steaming cauldron of woman? Okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的意思是只把我看成冒着热气的大姑娘？好吧。

yingyinNormal.en: And by this gesture, did you mean this is how I masturbate? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么做这个动作的意思是展示你如何自慰吗？不。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, the kids get picked on a little, but it toughens them up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我意思是，孩子们会有点不习惯，但这可以锻炼他们。

yingyinNormal.en: What does that mean? It means he is special and smart and nice and...
yingyinNormal.zh: 你什么意思？我的意思是，他很特别，有才，人好。

yingyinNormal.en: So, I guess you could call my mom or my sister, I mean as a reference.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许你可以打电话给我妈妈或者妹妹，我意思是说让她们作为推荐人。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, of course I chose that. I mean, I couldn't work in prison, and, uh…
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然我选择了后者。我的意思是，我，不能在监狱里工作，呃……

yingyinNormal.en: I was just going to sub in my turkey if you got in trouble, which, I mean...
yingyinNormal.zh: 我只是想着，万一你遇到麻烦，我就献上我的火鸡，我的意思是...

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: But that doesn't <highlight>mean</highlight> crucial ethical issues involving AI aren't at hand.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但这并不意味着涉及人工智能的关键伦理问题不在手边。

examination_example.sentence: Better grades can, by boosting figures like those, <highlight>mean</highlight> more money.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 通过提高这些数字，更好的成绩可能意味着更多的钱。

examination_example.sentence: Does that <highlight>mean</highlight> the writing is on the wall for all European royals, with their magnificent uniforms and majestic lifestyles?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这是否意味着所有衣着华丽、生活高贵的欧洲皇室成员将有大难了？

examination_example.sentence: Cattle rearing has been a major <highlight>means</highlight> of livelihood for the poor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 养牛一直是穷人的主要谋生手段。

examination_example.sentence: Electronic <highlight>means</highlight> of payment may be more efficient than a payments system based on paper.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 电子支付方式可能比基于纸张的支付系统更有效。

examination_example.sentence: A further concern is that the use of electronic <highlight>means</highlight> of payment leaves an electronic trail.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 另一个令人关切的问题是，使用电子支付方式会留下电子痕迹。

sense_info_list.en: intend something to occur or be the case
sense_info_list.zh: 意欲; 打算; 意图

examination_example.sentence: Airlines have simply changed the time a trip is <highlight>meant</highlight> to take.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 航空公司只是改变了旅行本来所需的时间。

examination_example.sentence: Every time we fail at something, we can choose to look for the lesson we're <highlight>meant</highlight> to learn.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 每当我们在某件事上失败时，我们可以选择寻找我们打算学习的教训。

examination_example.sentence: Any fair-minded assessment of the dangers of the deal must start by acknowledging that both sides <highlight>mean</highlight> well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 要对该协议的危险性进行公正的评估，首先必须承认双方的意图都是好的。

examination_example.sentence: Our visions of the future were largely — though by no <highlight>means</highlight> uniformly — glowingly positive.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们对未来的展望大体上是乐观的，尽管绝对不是一致的。

examination_example.sentence: Lengthy periods of economic stagnation or decline have almost always left society more <highlight>mean</highlight>-spirited and less inclusive.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 长期的经济停滞或衰退几乎总是让社会变得更加狭隘，包容性更低。

examination_example.sentence: If you do not receive any update within six months, it <highlight>means</highlight> that your application has not been successful.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在六个月内没有收到任何更新，这意味着你的申请没有成功。

examination_example.sentence: Even though it is not your style, that doesn't <highlight>mean</highlight> it is bad.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使这不是你的风格，也不意味着它不好。

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>meant</highlight> any inexpensive newspaper; perhaps more importantly it <highlight>meant</highlight> newspapers that could be bought in single copies on the street.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这意味着任何便宜的报纸；也许更重要的是，这意味着报纸可以在街上买到。

examination_example.sentence: The underlined expression "stomach it" in Paragraph 1 most probably <highlight>means</highlight> "manage without breakfast".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 第一段中下划线的表达“忍受”很可能是指“不吃早餐也行”。

examination_example.sentence: I <highlight>mean</highlight>, I don't see that much of them now as it is.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我是说，我现在已经不常见到他们了。

examination_example.sentence: The message "bridge out" would actually <highlight>mean</highlight> "Meet me."
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消息“bridgeout”实际上意味着“Meet me”。

examination_example.sentence: I picked up the stem cells in Providence, Rhode Island, and was <highlight>meant</highlight> to fly to Washington then back to London.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我在罗德岛的普罗维登斯取到了干细胞，并打算飞往华盛顿，然后返回伦敦。

examination_example.sentence: Ms.Jenkins <highlight>means</highlight> it for the board meeting next Monday.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Jenkins女士下周一董事会需要用它。

examination_example.sentence: Then came my tweens and teens, and <highlight>mean</highlight> girls and cool kids.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 那些刻薄的女生和酷酷的孩子一个接一个地出现在我的生活里。

examination_example.sentence: Anyone who opts to go on Alaska <highlight>Mean</highlight> River Time will live in harmony with the planet.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 任何选择阿拉斯加平均河时间的人都会与地球和谐相处。

word_usage.usage:
mean+to do sth. 意欲，打算”（不接动名词）： 
I'm sorry if I hurt your feelings; I didn't mean to.
假如我伤了你的感情，我很抱歉。我不是故意的。
有时用过去完成时，表示“本来打算”：
I had meant to leave on Monday, but I had stayed on.
我本想星期一走的，但又留下来了。
也可用mean + sb. +to do sth. 表示“打算让某人做某事”：
I didn't mean you to read the letter.
我没打算让你看这封信。

mean+doing sth. 表示“意味着”。
Reforming means developing. 
改革意味着发展。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 有意义的；重要的；有益的；严肃的；富有意味的
adj. 无意义的；无目的的；没有理智的
n. 意义；意思；含义；内涵；目的；隐含（或明白无误的）意思

word_family.mean: v. 指示；表示；意味；意欲；打算；引起；造成；应该做；被要求做；意思是

sense_info_list.en: intend to convey, indicate, or refer to a particular thing or notion

examination_example.sentence: This <highlight>means</highlight> that no new genes (基因) are put into the vegetables.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这意味着没有新的基因植入到蔬菜里。

examination_example.sentence: It <highlight>means</highlight> loving, respecting, obeying (服从), and taking care of one's parents in their old age.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它（孝）意思是敬爱、尊重、服从、晚年照顾父母双亲。

examination_example.sentence: It also <highlight>means</highlight> that they might be out on the street causing trouble.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这也意味着他们可能会流落街头，制造麻烦。

sense_info_list.en: intend something to occur or be the case

examination_example.sentence: I know she doesn't <highlight>mean</highlight> it personally, but she always complains that she doesn't have a home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我知道她绝无冒犯之意，但是她一直抱怨自己没有家。

word_usage.usage: mean后不可接否定的动词不定式not to do。
mean作“意味着”时，可接动名词，但不接动词不定式。
mean作“意欲，想要”时，可接动词不定式，但不接动名词。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 最普通用词。指文字或符号等所表示的各种明确的或含蓄的意义。
通常指暗含地、隐晦地表达意思。
